Directory intended to put some 3D body.

Center (AKA Origin, Pivot point...) of the player's body mesh have to be in the center of the head (aligned with eye position). Optimally, the head have to be inside a sphere of 0.1 unit in radius. If bigger, you'll need to manualy set the near clipping distance of the cameras.

The player body has to look in the same direction as the negative Z axis.

Animation :  easy animation handleling will be provided in the future.

No physics is applied to the player's body mesh. the Virtual body provide a btCapsuleShape for the player. It has the player height and a radius of 0.5 metters.
